Class Logger

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.miloss.fgsms.common.Logger

  • public class Logger
extends Object
    Mirrors Apache Log4j and acts as a wrapper. Modeled after the OWASP Enterprise Security API ESAPI Primary function, protect against log forging
